      "text": "PLACES OF CORRUPTION Agreed Lists shall be prepared of points and places where corrupt practices are prevalent. It may be emphasized that these are not lists of all those points and places where is scope of likelihood of corruption but only of those where corruption is believed to exist in substantial measure. 19 Substituted vide CBI Crime Manual 2020. 20 Substituted vide CBI Crime Manual 2020. 21 Substituted vide CBI Crime Manual 2020. 22 Inserted vide CBI Crime Manual 2020.",
